channel.title: How to download anything you want free
channel.description:
Want a program, game, song, etc but can't afford it? Then follow these steps.
First you need a torrent client, I suggest utorrent, which can get from utorrent.com.
Now you need a torrents site to download from.
Here are some well known ones.
[code] www.mininova.org www.isohunt.com www.thepiratebay.com www.torrentreactor.net www.torrentz.com[/code]
I suggest using www.mininova.org.
Once you are on the site search for any program, song, etc you want and start your download.
Scan everything you download with virusscan.jotti.org.
